# Protos Web — Cursor entrypoint
#
# PRODUCTION CODE ONLY. Rules guard the codebase — not the product roadmap.
# Standards: .cursor/rules/*.mdc (alwaysApply)

Read first:
- .cursor/rules/protos-web.mdc       — stack, deploy, Supabase-only
- .cursor/rules/dom-canvas-layers.mdc — showcase vs site chrome (mandatory for 3D/UI)
- .cursor/rules/fix-not-remove.mdc   — do not delete working features
- docs/architecture.md               — zones, backend ownership
- docs/security.md                   — secret placement

Do not duplicate long memory dumps in this repo. Protos-Agent is admin-panel only — ignore it when coding here.
